[Student "S"]
{With 12 points and five \Ss, when NORTH hears her partner open 1NT she knows 
there is a game - either 3NT or 4\S.

NORTH first transfers SOUTH to \Ss, then jumps to 3NT, giving SOUTH the choice. 

SOUTH has three \Ss, so he chooses 4\S, taking the 8-card Major fit.}

